play.it (2.25.4-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * New upstream release.
  * Add dependencies (Recommends) on the packages providing game scripts.
  * Add packages required to run tests to the build-dependencies list.
  * Drop pandoc from the list of build-dependencies.
  * Update upstream project Web page URL.
  * Update debian/watch to no longer rely on parsing GitLab URLs.
  * Update debian/copyright with the upstream authors list.
  * Bump Standards-Version to 4.6.2

